{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLInputElement: invalid event","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement\"><code>HTMLInputElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/files\"><code>files</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/labels\"><code>labels</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/multiple\"><code>multiple</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/webkitdirectory\"><code>webkitdirectory</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/webkitEntries\"><code>webkitEntries</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/checkValidity\"><code>checkValidity()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/reportValidity\"><code>reportValidity()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select\"><code>select()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setCustomValidity\"><code>setCustomValidity()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setRangeText\"><code>setRangeText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/setSelectionRange\"><code>setSelectionRange()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/showPicker\"><code>showPicker()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/stepDown\"><code>stepDown()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/stepUp\"><code>stepUp()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>事件</summary><ol><li><em><code>invalid</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/search_event\"><code>search</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/select_event\"><code>select</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>若一个可提交元素在检查有效性时，不符合对它的约束条件，则会触发 <strong><code>invalid</code></strong> 事件。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th>冒泡</th>\n      <td>否</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>可取消</th>\n      <td>是</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>接口</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>事件处理程序属性</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.oninvalid</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>这个事件可用于展示提交表单时所出现的问题的概览。当表单提交时，若任一表单控件无效，则会触发 <code>invalid</code> 事件。对可提交元素有效性的检查是在提交父元素 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> 之前或调用父元素 <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> 或元素自己的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/Forms#constraint_validation_api\"><code>checkValidity()</code></a> 方法之后。</p>\n<p>这个事件不会在 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/blur_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">blur (en-US)</a></code> 事件中触发。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>如果表单提交时有无效值，检查可提交元素时发现了错误，则 <code>invalid</code> 事件会在那个无效元素上触发。在这个例子中，当输入无效值触发 <code>invalid</code> 事件时，这个无效值被记录下来。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>form</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">action</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Enter an integer between 1 and 10: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>number<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">min</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">max</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>10<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">required</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>input</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>submit<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">value</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>submit<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>ul</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>form</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>log<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> input <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'input'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> log <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'log'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ninput<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'invalid'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> logValue<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">logValue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  log<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">+=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"结果","title":"结果","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"示例\" id=\"frame_examples\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-invalid","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.HTMLInputElement.invalid_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLInputElement.invalid_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLInputElement/invalid_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>HTML <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> 元素</li>\n  <li>相关事件：<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/submit_ev